        "heading": "Our Workshop",
        "heading_em": "in Sihor",
        "body_1": "The Kansawala workshop has stood on Kansara Bazar Road in Sihor, Bhavnagar since 1945. Sihor is one of Gujarat's oldest centres of kansara (metalworking) craft — a town whose artisans have practiced this trade for hundreds of years.",
